Licensees may view, adapt, modify and redistribute SSM-OSGV technical data, however, any technical data derived from SSM-OSGV technical data must also be governed by the same SSM-OSGV license and made available to the public through an SSM-OSGV approved medium (e.g. osgv.org).

Except when the interface specification remains intact: the new part conforms to its source control / specification control / interface control drawings; only then the private entities may retain the proprietary status of design."
